nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
A bearded man with red facial hair wearing a yellow straw hat and dark coat in Van Gogh's self-portrait style, slowly and continuously transforms into a space astronaut. The transformation flows like liquid paint - his beard fades away strand by strand, the yellow hat melts and reforms smoothly into a silver space helmet, dark coat gradually lightens and restructures into a white spacesuit. The background swirling brushstrokes slowly organize and clarify into realistic stars and space, with Earth appearing gradually in the distance. Every change happens in seamless waves, maintaining visual continuity throughout the metamorphosis.

Consistent soft lighting throughout, medium close-up maintaining same framing, central composition stays fixed, gentle color temperature shift from warm to cool, gradual contrast increase, smooth style transition from painterly to photorealistic. Static camera with subtle slow zoom, emphasizing the flowing transformation process without abrupt changes.

nodes.title: Note: About 4 Steps LoRA
widgets_values: Using the Wan2.2 Lighting LoRA will result in the loss of video dynamics, but it will reduce the generation time. This template provides two workflows, and you can enable one as needed.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Use reference image 1 as the starting appearance and reference image 2 as the final state.
An anthropomorphic sloth character, maintaining the same facial features, body proportions, fur texture, clothing style, and identity throughout the transformation.
The sloth begins as a calm, stylish street character, standing in a human-like pose, wearing a dark jacket, white t-shirt, jeans, sunglasses, and multiple gold chains.
The environment gradually transitions from an elegant urban street setting into a nighttime DJ stage.
Lighting slowly shifts from natural daylight to dramatic blue and purple club lighting with haze and neon accents.
In the final state, the sloth becomes a DJ, wearing over-ear headphones, hands placed on a DJ mixer, confident and relaxed expression.
Strong character consistency, realistic fur details, cinematic lighting, shallow depth of field, smooth temporal transition, subtle motion, high detail, cinematic atmosphere, dynamic but controlled movement.
